{"tid":1763383,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【賭王又有索孫女】何超鳳細女何倩珩倫敦ball登場 家底厚讀哥倫比亞大學拎獎金","createTime":"2019-11-30T09:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T08:28:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd3f4e65b3462b042d96522bad27808797e44d1","tid":1763383,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"賭王何鴻燊三、四房頻頻抱孫，分別有三房孻仔猷啟兩年抱兩生兩女Tittania及Tylia，而四房大女何超盈及孻仔何猷君就於8月及10月生了孫女Andrey Rose及孫仔Ronaldo，而Ronaldo更是賭王首位男孫，中文名取名何廣燊。<br />\n三、四房為賭王添第三代新成員，其實二房外孫女已亭亭玉立，當中超鳳的大女何鍶珩（Beatrice）就較為傳媒所認識，她愛在社交平台展示她的性感三點式水着，近月更開了IG，高調公開有美國大隻仔男友Greg，更不時放閃，不介意私生活曝光。昨日，她就在IG又有新帖文，貼了一張與母親何超鳳及阿姨何超瓊身在倫敦去ball的圖片，同場還有甚少露面的妹妹何倩珩（Gillian），Gillian甚少在香港出席社交場合，亦不似姐姐般公開社交平台分享生活點滴。<br />\n現年21歲的Gillian就身穿湖水綠的deep V開衩長裙，而Beatrice就化重妝，以一身紅裙裝身，Beatrice就在IG留言多謝大會的邀請，兩姊妹現居紐約，為了活動專誠飛去倫敦，令她有一個難忘的感恩節。不少網友都有讚她靚，亦有友人留言「4 beauty sisters」指四人似姊妹。Gillian早年的外型都略帶baby fat，現在女大十八變，外型斯文小淑女，性格雖沒家姐般外向，不過她亦是高材生一名，與家姐一樣就讀美國長春藤名牌大學，她現就讀哥倫比亞大學三年級，修讀文科學士，明年畢業。她在校內成績不俗，連續3年在校內入Dean's list，即獲學院嘉許她的傑出學術成績。雖然是出身家族坐擁百億賭王王國的富三代，但她讀書成績好，由讀中學年代因GCSE成績好已拎獎學金，去到哥倫比亞大學第一年，亦已拎校內的「John Jay Scholar」獎學金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575099328_e988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575099328_e988.jpg&h=c062072b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超鳳與超瓊去了紐約過感恩節，超鳳的兩個女兒何倩珩（左一）與何鍶珩（右一）在紐約居住，當然有現身陪伴。（IG圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575099422_3260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575099422_3260.jpg&h=12f042a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191130/60327433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60327433&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipfxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=74d3416e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60327433&h=12f65c6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191130/60327433</a>"},{"pid":"7b0cd5164b44d67fc3dc6304a85c59c1f2f34141","tid":1763383,"uid":7903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"索？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bb7ed656d07500931ae2081e77e164e14b50eb","tid":1763383,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4df0a36609d680f9096605858b8ca26e2f9165c","tid":1763383,"uid":169071,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"索你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb0ade086c388271bd04c4e60e25e87ab623be4","tid":1763383,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"算啦 佢份人幾好 唔好攻擊佢啦"},{"pid":"99948ccbe2b27c06f881b4107a77da8138ce488d","tid":1763383,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efb0ade086c388271bd04c4e60e25e87ab623be4","tid":1763383,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"算啦 佢份人幾好 唔好攻擊佢啦"},"citedBy":1,